body:
1. {{champion:27}} 
Likely on his W since that&#039;s currently the least noticeable part of his kit overall. Would be cool if it Grounded enemies and would really work since it&#039;s Adhesive Glue.

2. {{champion:420}} 
Likely on her Q since it&#039;s the only move it would really work on. Tentacle Slam would slam the enemy into ground to make them unable to dash or blink. Would make her a little less completely raw damage.

3. {{champion:57}} 
Likely on his E. It would help Maokai against ganks since his E could Ground them upon exploding, giving him time to run from the gank.

4. {{champion:78}} 
Might be overkill with her W, but I think it would be cool if we pushed Poppy into the &quot;Anti-Mobility&quot; niche with her Q applying Grounded. Would allow Riot to push her in a direction besides just a generalist Fighter/Tank with a disengage ultimate.
